description: The purpose of this skill is to educate citizens of the United States of its history with a fun and interactive way. More Questions will be added Weekly to enhance the skill.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, open u. s. trivia game
Alexa, start u. s. trivia game
Alexa, begin u. s. trivia game
name: United States' Trivia Game
shortDescription: A game that test people's knowledge of United States' History. An educational and fun game that people of all ages can play.
